MISBEHAVING LADY trailed for half a mile, moved wide into the stretch rallying. ROSE LEGACY steadied inside rival at the eighth pole and angled out and closed. An objection by the rider of ROSE LEGACY against the rider of FRIEDER FANATIC for interference in the stretch was dismissed.
